{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347940/extras/Sea_of_Survivors_Trailer.gif?t=1730005364\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fight hordes of swashbucklers and sea monsters. Explore an open world scattered with treacherous islands, lost treasures and mysterious curses. Combine powerful relics and upgrades to become more powerful and test yourself against fierce enemies, epic bosses and the sea itself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2347940/extras/03.png?t=1730005364\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Sail a ship that can never stop moving, navigate and explore an open world with distinct biomes and factions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Destroy thousands of pirates, sea monsters and outlast horrors of the deep during action packed 20 minute runs</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Discover lost islands, raid them for their treasure and face off against the foes that protect them</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Rescue unique crew members with randomized traits and recruit them to help you on your journey</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Find powerful treasures and relics. Combine them and discover different synergies with every run.\u00a0</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Collect doubloons from fallen enemies and use them upgrade your ship permanently\u00a0</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Complete bounties to unlock achievements and more content</p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Cost of doing business","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2347940/f630a2e72b801a8c206bc1b9f9ea84be1a073c19.jpg"},{"name":"Armsman","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2347940/dc83650d8d995e5f0c718a58e616b129